---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About me | Vipul Zope">
  <article class="max-w-[650px] mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">About me</h1>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed">

      <p>i don't really know much yet. all i know is that the more i learn and the more i build, the more interesting life becomes – that's been an incredibly optimistic realization.</p>

      <p>i've been a conductor of chaos since i was a kid. as a School Band Leader, i played drums and bass for annual parades – learning the high-stakes timing of live performance. i spent my teens as a Pro-Gamer learning strategy under pressure. i model my execution style after Rohit Sharma: calm leadership, selfless strategy, and relentless power when it's time to hit.</p>

      <p>i've known since i was 13 that building was going to be the first chapter of my life. since then, i've dropshipped, ran Minecraft servers, played at competitive levels of online gaming, built communities from scratch, managed large-scale recruitment operations, navigated regulatory crises, and scaled teams. i also have a list of dozens and dozens of failed ventures that could fill up a whole page.</p>

      <p>after dropping out... <em>wait, i didn't</em>. i finished my <strong>Computer Engineering degree (Honours in Data Science)</strong> and then took time off to handle a critical family medical emergency. that chapter is closed, and i'm back in the arena with full force.</p>

    </div>

    <hr class="my-8 border-[var(--color-border)]" />

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-4">Experiences</h2>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-2">Present</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">COO @ Stealth AI Company</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">after selling SwipeLabs to an AI company, i now work there as the COO. active angel investor in 100+ companies (and growing).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-2">Past</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Founder @ SwipeLabs.io</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">blessed to have grown to millions in revenue & 25 FT employees before exiting in 2025. served 100+ of the fastest-growing tech companies.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Growth @ Placecom</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">managed hiring pipelines for IBM, HP, Bentley, Mercedes-Benz, Bosch, TCS and 30+ global giants.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Founding Ops @ OP OFFICIALS</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">scaled a community to 110k subscribers and 74k discord members from scratch.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Lead @ StreamEase</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">built a network of 78+ creators for Loco, Rooter, JioGames, Chingari and Rumble.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Regulatory Exit (2022)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">navigated the 2022 Govt ban which forced an exit after 20 months of growth and partnerships with Monster Energy, Redbull, Spinbot, and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Other Ventures</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">various indie SaaS projects, dropshipping, Minecraft servers, competitive online gaming, and others (NDA).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-8 border-[var(--color-border)]" />

    <section>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text)]">
        if you are building something massive in Physical AI, Robotics, or Data Infrastructure — <a href="https://cal.com/vipulzope">let's talk</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm">
        <a href="mailto:contactzope@gmail.com">contactzope@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </article>
</Layout>
